genresAdvancedInfo.name: muzica copii
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Muzica copii is a music genre aimed at children. It is characterized by its simple melodies, catchy rhythms, and fun lyrics. The music is often used in educational settings to teach children about language, numbers, and other basic concepts. Muzica copii is also used for entertainment purposes, with popular children's songs being played at parties and events. The genre is an important part of childhood memories for many Romanians.
